40Mt 11:4 Jesus answered, "Go back and tell John what you are hearing and seeing�� 
40Mt 11:5 the blind can see, the lame can walk, those who suffer from dreaded skin diseases are made clean, the deaf hear, the dead are brought back to life, and the Good News is preached to the poor. 
