40Mt 23:1 Then Jesus spoke to the crowds and to his disciples. 
40Mt 23:2 "The teachers of the Law and the Pharisees are the authorized interpreters of Moses' Law. 
40Mt 23:3 So you must obey and follow everything they tell you to do; do not, however, imitate their actions, because they don't practice what they preach. 
