40Mt 23:5 They do everything so that people will see them. Look at the straps with scripture verses on them which they wear on their foreheads and arms, and notice how large they are! Notice also how long are the tassels on their cloaks! 
40Mt 23:6 They love the best places at feasts and the reserved seats in the synagogues; 
40Mt 23:7 they love to be greeted with respect in the marketplaces and to have people call them 'Teacher.' 
