40Mt 24:48 But if he is a bad servant, he will tell himself that his master will not come back for a long time, 
40Mt 24:49 and he will begin to beat his fellow servants and to eat and drink with drunkards. 
40Mt 24:50 Then that servant's master will come back one day when the servant does not expect him and at a time he does not know. 
