40Mt 25:8 Then the foolish ones said to the wise ones, 'Let us have some of your oil, because our lamps are going out.' 
40Mt 25:9 'No, indeed,' the wise ones answered, 'there is not enough for you and for us. Go to the store and buy some for yourselves.' 
