42Lk 2:3 Everyone, then, went to register himself, each to his own hometown. 
42Lk 2:4 Joseph went from the town of Nazareth in Galilee to the town of Bethlehem in Judea, the birthplace of King David. Joseph went there because he was a descendant of David. 
