42Lk 4:31 Then Jesus went to Capernaum, a town in Galilee, where he taught the people on the Sabbath. 
42Lk 4:32 They were all amazed at the way he taught, because he spoke with authority. 
42Lk 4:33 In the synagogue was a man who had the spirit of an evil demon in him; he screamed out in a loud voice, 
