43Jn 11:17 When Jesus arrived, he found that Lazarus had been buried four days before. 
43Jn 11:18 Bethany was less than two miles from Jerusalem, 
43Jn 11:19 and many Judeans had come to see Martha and Mary to comfort them about their brother's death. 
43Jn 11:20 When Martha heard that Jesus was coming, she went out to meet him, but Mary stayed in the house. 
43Jn 11:21 Martha said to Jesus, "If you had been here, Lord, my brother would not have died! 
43Jn 11:22 But I know that even now God will give you whatever you ask him for." 
